longBusinessSummary: Electromedical Technologies, Inc., a bioelectronics manufacturing and marketing company, provides medical devices for pain management in the United States. Its products include WellnessPro Plus, a bioelectronics therapy prescription device to relieve chronic and acute pain. Electromedical Technologies, Inc. is headquartered in Scottsdale, Arizona.
